-- Lea Salonga Discussess Third Café Carlyle Engagement (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-05-24T18:19:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-24/lea-salonga-discussess-third-caf%C3%A9-carlyle-engagement-audio-.html
Lea Salonga, a singer and actress who
has appeared in broadway musicals and several films, discusses 
her third engagement at the Café Carlyle and her involvement in 
"Allegiance," a new musical in development to open in New York 
City in 2014. Salonga talks with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and 
Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 11:49
 